data.description: This lovely four bedroom, four bath home combines the timeless charm of hardwood floors with the modern convenience of ample storage and outdoor privacy. Upon entering, you are greeted by the warmth of hardwood floors that extend throughout the house, setting the stage for the charming details that follow. The heart of this home is undoubtedly the kitchen, which is not only equipped with stainless steel appliances but also boasts a large island, ideal for meal prep and casual dining. This space effortlessly opens onto a spacious, covered composite deck, complete with billowing curtains and ceiling fans, providing an extended area for entertainment or relaxation. The deck leads to a beautifully designed paver patio, enhancing the outdoor living experience. Architectural elegance is on display in the large family room, where a cathedral ceiling and a wood-burning fireplace, flanked by large windows, create an inviting and majestic space. Convenience is further emphasized on the main floor with an office boasting glimmering French doors, a bonus room that connects to the office, formal dining room, and a half bath. Sauntering up the overlook staircase, each of the four bedrooms offers a unique blend of comfort and style, with spacious designs that cater to both relaxation and creativity. The natural light dances across the floors, enhancing the overall ambiance and making every room inviting. The primary suite is a retreat within itself, featuring a walk-in closet and an en-suite bathroom equipped with double sinks, a soaking tub, and a stall shower. The laundry area on this level adds to the conveniences of this lovely home. Additional features such as a partially finished basement with a bar and utility room are coupled with a considerable storage area which could be finished for additional entertaining space. The house also boasts a two car garage with additional storage space. This feature is perfect for those who love to keep their living spaces clutter-free or for hobbyists who need extra room for their equipment. Surrounding the property is a fully-fenced yard, offering privacy and a haven for outdoor activities. Whether you are hosting a family barbecue, enjoying a peaceful morning with a cup of coffee, or providing a play area for children and pets, this yard caters to it all. This home is a harmonious blend of functionality and comfort, making it an ideal choice for anyone looking for a serene living space designed to accommodate modern living. Close to major highways, transportation, shopping and dining. Make an appointment today to view this lovely home!
